I'm going to be talking about our other big game, which was called Sorcery.

6
00:00:26,268 --> 00:00:30,511
Hopefully you've heard of it, hopefully you've played it, so this talk will make some kind

7
00:00:30,551 --> 00:00:31,231
of sense to you.

8
00:00:32,152 --> 00:00:37,475
If you haven't, I'll try to be clear, and Rock Paper Shotgun called it their RPG of

